&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Function:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design, architecture, development, and delivery of medical-grade mobile applications and SDKs using Java, Kotlin, and Kotlin&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design, development, and maintenance of high-quality Android applications and SDKs using Java, Kotlin, and KMM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical leadership and architectural guidance to Android engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product management, cloud engineering, UX, QA, and other cross-functional teams to define technical solutions and product roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive technical design discussions, establish engineering standards, and promote best practices across the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate customer, business, and market requirements into scalable, secure, and maintainable mobile solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the integration of mobile applications with cloud-based platforms, APIs, and backend services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scope projects, decompose work into deliverable modules, estimate effort, and support program planning activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor, coach, and support engineers through code reviews, technical guidance, and knowledge sharing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own application quality, performance, scalability, and maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive troubleshooting, root cause analysis, and resolution of complex technical issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate emerging technologies, develop proofs of concept, and recommend solution alternatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present technical concepts, architectures, and solutions to customers, partners, leadership, and stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure adherence to Agile development practices and contribute to continuous process improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other duties as required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
